{
  "stem": "24364.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I went-- I went to a-- first, I tried at my school in my hometown, but obviously, the German school was closed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Czech school, the-- the mean guy who was my Czech professor was now the director, who had hated me at that time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when I came to the school and said, hey, I would like, you know, to be able to make my matura or baccalaureate, he said, no way.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have German schools, and you better stop doing that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They might even deport you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll never forget that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He told me that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then I found a lawyer in my hometown who had a friend who was director of a school in Prague.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was very lucky that I had those three months in the Czech school, because at that time, this German papers-- I mean papers from German school, you were really in deep trouble in-- you know, after the war.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had those three months from the Czech school, which had my last report card.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all they always demanded was your last report card, so I could give them that last report card, which wasn't very good, but that was unimportant.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had passed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so what they allowed me to do, which was very nice, really, was take a test in every subject, rather than go through the whole matura.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- there were like 13 subjects, and I had to take a test in every subject.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I studied like crazy, and I guess I did it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And people were very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They really helped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, most professors were super-nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
